Package com.itko.lisa.remote.plumbing

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAgentEventListener
    Classes registered to receive agent events must implement this interface
    IAssemblyExtension
    A hook in the broker that is invoked just after a frame is received from one of the agents or consoles and just before it is assembled with other frames.
    IStatsEventListener
    Classes registered to receive statistics events must implement this interface
    ITransactionEventListener
    Classes registered to received transaction events must implement this interface
